{"TopicId":221015,"ForumId":11,"TopicTitle":"FOR SCIENCE! arrives December 19th","CreatedByName":"Intercept Games","CreatedById":210281,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T17:55:24Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Intercept Games","CreatedById":210281,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T17:55:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAttention Kerbonauts!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027re ecstatic to share that....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFOR SCIENCE! WILL BE OUT DECEMBER 19th, 2023!!!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221063\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.38\u0022 data-unique=\u00226iywfljfb\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP2_ForScience_ReleaseDate_Small_V1.png\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_11/KSP2_ForScience_ReleaseDate_Small_V1.png.f270280afd1dc9525c919c223ef67a85.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck out our \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/220137-introducing-for-science-major-content-update-out-in-december/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Elast news post\u003C/a\u003E for information on features to expect! And stay tuned for an all-new Dev Chat later this week that dives deep into everything this milestone update has to offer!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ll share more details about global release timing when we get closer to launch. We can\u0027t wait for you all to get your hands on For Science!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rebel-1","CreatedById":170896,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T17:57:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally! We waited. It remains to wait for optimization and career mode.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:01:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n20 days\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WelshSteW","CreatedById":202966,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:04:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYES!! HERE WE GO!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Urus28","CreatedById":182121,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:14:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hope this will give KSP2 a new start =)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"PDCWolf","CreatedById":58026,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:14:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad we have a date, not glad it\u0027s right there with the holidays. Not for me or players, but for the capacity the team might have to deploy hotfixes if something goes wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope those 2 months since it was \u0022locked in\u0022 have been well spent in actual testing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TechieV","CreatedById":229200,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:23:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224343577\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221015\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221701280872\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n20 days\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know! It\u2019s so close!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:kiss:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_kiss.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:kiss:\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NexusHelium","CreatedById":230359,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:26:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLegitimately, I can\u0027t stop silently pumping my fist.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:40:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t wait to see new parts\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sans","CreatedById":214540,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T18:42:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy life in pause for the next 20 days\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wheehaw Kerman","CreatedById":223516,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T19:01:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally looking forward to the dev chat - it\u2019ll hopefully settle a lot of the speculation we\u2019ve been seeing (and trigger a whole bunch more).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T19:13:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224343586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221015\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221701281658\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PDCWolf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n57 minutes ago, PDCWolf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad we have a date, not glad it\u0027s right there with the holidays. Not for me or players, but for the capacity the team might have to deploy hotfixes if something goes wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope those 2 months since it was \u0022locked in\u0022 have been well spent in actual testing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAgreed.\u00A0 The team (if memory serves) goes on Christmas break like the 21st.\u00A0 2 days of wiggle room for potential hot-fixes is not good, especially when you consider how many people might buy this as a Christmas present for themselves or others.\u00A0 Hopefully they tested this out fully by release.\u00A0 If not...good grief and my condolences on anyone whose plans get cancelled to deal with it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Margoth","CreatedById":227390,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T19:13:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA nice Christmas present, thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"viperfan7","CreatedById":740,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T21:34:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJoystick support going to come with this update?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T21:52:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeeeeeeuuuh! Cant wait to hear details. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Clayel","CreatedById":223206,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T21:52:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nnice, before christmas!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mitokandria","CreatedById":222458,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-29T21:59:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo plan survives first contact. I\u0027ll be taking time off for the update/release, but I fully expect it to not \u0022stick the landing\u0022 before the holiday break. Still, progress is progress and I look forward to getting my hands on it anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-11-29T22:00:22Z\u0022 title=\u002211/29/2023 10:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Nov 29\u0022\u003ENovember 29, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Mitokandria\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cytauri","CreatedById":223905,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T00:26:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, I\u2019m surprised and got a little bit hopeful which reminded me of when the KSP 2 trailer came out (I was full of joy.) Hopefully, this will be the update that restarts KSP 2 back to the times of when we were excited for this game and not disappointed with every dev update, because I feel a little bit excited.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T00:39:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224343574\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221015\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221701280524\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210281\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Intercept Games\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Intercept Games said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0We can\u0027t wait for you all to get your hands on For Science!m\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, obviously you can\u2026 until the 19\u003Csup\u003Eth\u003C/sup\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224343586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221015\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221701281658\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258026\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PDCWolf\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, PDCWolf said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGlad we have a date, not glad it\u0027s right there with the holidays. Not for me or players, but for the capacity the team might have to deploy hotfixes if something goes wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHotfixes? That sounds wildly speculative.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stephensan","CreatedById":222320,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T00:50:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsoup!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Casellina X","CreatedById":226034,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T00:55:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight on time for me to be away from my computer for 3 weeks. Guess I\u0027ll have my eye on the forums when the time comes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T01:10:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224343663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221015\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221701304761\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHotfixes? That sounds wildly speculative.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s speculative that newly released software might need to be fixed?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-30T02:25:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-content